horse day. And the horses used to be dressed up - corporation horses and all like them you know. And - they used to - all the corporation horses and the - stores and all them, they used to have horses, you know, the railway - they all had horses and they 
dressed them up and it was called bell horse day - we used to call it bell horse day - and she says when you was born the bell horses was passing the door. I always remember the first of May.
