\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5265281\charrsid16398449  her at finish, but she was called Jate }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6038262\charrsid16398449 O}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
