- gave her a bet of the morning - he worked at Paddy Reid's - that was a bleach works down at lane and - he got to know that this horse had won and he came home to see had she drawed the money. And - instead of putting - she hadn't put the bet on but she 
was drunk up the stairs in bed. And he went upstairs and pulled her out of bed and kicked her to death upstairs you see. Yes.
