It was the same street - this is the same street you know. Well we - I went there when I was - as I say - three years - about three years old. That was at sixty-two, Rossall Street there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5445667 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5265281\charrsid16398449 How long did you stay there?
