was thirteen and then I went to - I started down Pendleton pit. And - when I was seventeen I got - I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11339473 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
