Oh no, no, mother always used to - she didn't - never for me - she used to mend 'em you know, seen her do it, we'd no money to buy suits then like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5445667 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5265281\charrsid16398449 Were they always new clothes?
