No. We, no. Sometimes we used to get - give 'em - buy 'em cheap you know in these shops - brokers shops and things. There's here - we call 'em brokers you know same as that - across the road there - clothing place. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5445667 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5265281\charrsid16398449 Usually local shops were they?
