Oh he - we used to get them put on - it was only fourpence a set. Aye - we wore clogs - always wore clogs. And the wife wore clogs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5445667 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5265281\charrsid16398449 Do you remember when you had new clothes or shoes - what time of the year?

