 - doing anything - if you were - wouldn't do right you know, we used to - in the schoolyard when we perhaps pulled one another to pieces you know and they wouldn't - they wouldn't like us to do that. And - they used to chastise us that way you see. And t
hen sometimes the teacher'd turn her back you know and then we was at it again and - and she'd - she'd come in again and catch us and then we were - we was for it again.
