Oh no, no, not - nothing like that love. No. I don't - I've heard bits - my mother was off - my mother was always born - she was born on the first of - April. That was all fool's - that was fools day of course, supposed to have b
een. But - you never could catch her. She could }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9836352\charrsid16398449 neither}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5265281\charrsid16398449 
 read nor write but - if you was to go in and try to catch her like - what's on the floor, mum, pick it up. And there was nothing there you know, so, you're April Fool and all like that if you used to 
