No, just the one suit - I don't remember ever having a suit only that one me mother went and bought - the little sailor suit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5445667 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5265281\charrsid16398449 Didn't you ever go to Sunday school or anything like that?
